        <abstract> 
<p>Is satisfied with CD’s arrangement with Murray for Appleton’s to pay $50 [pounds or dollars!?] for stereo plates and clichés of 21 woodblocks for CD’s new book [<hi rend="italic">Expression</hi>, see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">8217</hi>]. Has ordered 5000 sets of plate impressions from Robert Cooke at Murray’s.</p> 
        </abstract>
